        "last_activity_date": 1459874188,
        "creation_date": 1459874188,
        "body": "<p>This is how to get all candidates for a specific task (<code>taskId<\/code>).<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; users = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\nList&lt;String&gt; groups = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\nList&lt;IdentityLink&gt; links = taskService.getIdentityLinksForTask(taskId);\nfor (IdentityLink link : links) {\n    if (IdentityLinkType.CANDIDATE.equals(link.getType())) {\n        String userId = link.getUserId();\n        if (userId != null) {\n            users.add(userId);\n        }\n        String groupId = link.getGroupId();\n        if (groupId != null) {\n            groups.add(groupId);\n        }\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
